{"iti54:0.1":"Itivuttaka 54 ","iti54:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti54:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti54:0.4":"Pathamaesanasutta ","iti54:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti54:2.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, esana. ","iti54:2.2":"Katama tisso? ","iti54:2.3":"Kamesana, bhavesana, brahmacariyesana—","iti54:2.4":"ima kho, bhikkhave, tisso esana”ti. ","iti54:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti54:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti54:3.1":"“Samahito sampajano, ","iti54:3.2":"sato buddhassa savako; ","iti54:3.3":"Esana ca pajanati, ","iti54:3.4":"esanananca sambhavam. ","iti54:4.1":"Yattha ceta nirujjhanti, ","iti54:4.2":"magganca khayagaminam; ","iti54:4.3":"Esananam khaya bhikkhu, ","iti54:4.4":"nicchato parinibbuto”ti. ","iti54:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti54:5.2":"Pancamam. "}